---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
import { NAME, USERNAME } from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title={NAME}>
  <main>
    <section>
      <h1 style="color: var(--accent);" class="h0">{NAME}</h1>
      <p>
        hi!!! welcome to my little corner of the internet! i'm <strong
          >{NAME}</strong
        >, a hobbyist designer and maker! i really love open source and i enjoy
        making apps for the <a href="https://gnome.org/">GNOME</a> and <a
          href="https://elementary.io/">elementary</a
        > ecosystems. i also love dabbling in app development for Apple platforms
        whenever i get the chance!
      </p>
      <p>
        this website is where i'll eventually showcase the work i'm proud of
        (once i actually finish some), and share projects and people i find
        cool! feel free to take a look around! i think you'll find some really
        lovely stuff!
      </p>
      <hr />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>about me</h2>
      <p>
        i like making designs that are capable but easy to understand. a big
        part of design to me is it being a medium to make the content
        shine—whilst also having character.
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          True simplicity is derived from so much more than just the absence of
          clutter and ornamentation. It's about bringing order to complexity.
        </p>
        <cite>— jony ive</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <hr />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>what i've done</h2>
      <p>some things i've worked on in the past</p>
      <h3><a href="https://buildtheearth.net">BuildTheEarth.net</a></h3>
      <p>
        a project that aims to recreate the Earth in Minecraft. the main project
        is a Guinness World Record holder for the largest Minecraft project in
        the world!
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Middle East Team</strong> — i worked as the system administrator
          for the minecraft server and now i oversee the middle eastern team as a
          manager.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Support Staff</strong> — volunteered as support staff from 2020
          to 2023, helping users with technical issues.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3><a href="https://github.com/Avdan-OS/">AvdanOS</a></h3>
      <p>a Linux desktop environment project based on a concept by Avdan.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>UI Designer</strong> — worked from 2022 to 2023 creating UI mockups
          and design systems for the desktop
        </li>
      </ul>
      <hr />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>cool projects</h2>
      <p>here are some great projects that i love and/or work with:</p>
      <div class="card-grid large">
        <a href="https://elementary.io/" class="card">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://elementary.io/images/screenshots/desktop.jpg"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">elementaryOS</h3>
          <p class="card-description">
            a beautiful, accessible, well-designed linux distribution.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/greeeen-dev/natsumi-browser" class="card">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://github.com/greeeen-dev/natsumi-browser/blob/main/images/main.webp?raw=true"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">Natsumi Browser</h3>
          <p class="card-description">
            an awesome userchrome theme for firefox and forks.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://gnome.org/" class="card">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://os.gnome.org/assets/nightly.webp"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">GNOME</h3>
          <p class="card-description">
            a linux desktop ecosystem, with great design and accessibility.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <hr />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>cool people</h2>
      <p>
        here are some really talented people i admire and love collaborating
        with:
      </p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <a href="https://fizzyizzy05.dev/" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/85719751?v=4"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">Izzy</h3>
        </a>
        <a href="https://zoeythewitch.page/" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/239873844?v=4"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">Zoey</h3>
        </a>
        <a href="https://tesk.page/" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/50847364?v=4"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">TheEvilSkeleton</h3>
        </a>
        <a href="https://kramo.page/" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/93832451?v=4"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">kramo</h3>
        </a>
        <a href="https://jamie.garden/" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://gitlab.gnome.org/uploads/-/system/user/avatar/112136/avatar.png"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">Jamie</h3>
        </a>
        <a href="https://greeeen.dev/" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/41323182?v=4"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">green</h3>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/heliguy4599" class="card horizontal">
          <img
            class="card-image"
            src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/95997226?v=4"
            alt=""
          />
          <h3 class="card-title">Heliguy</h3>
        </a>
      </div>
      <hr />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>find me</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href={`https://github.com/${USERNAME}`}>github</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://mastodon.social/@linuxjava7">mastodon</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <hr />
    </section>

    <p>thanks for visiting!</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
